INFO  2023-05-25 08:08:29,597 [1    ] oft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command - Executed DbCommand (44ms) [Parameters=[@__language_Name_1='?' (Size = 128)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [AbpLanguages] AS [a]
        WHERE ([a].[TenantId] IS NULL) AND [a].[Name] = @__language_Name_1) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)

SELECT [b].[Id], [b].[CreationTime], [b].[CreatorUserId], [b].[DeleterUserId], [b].[DeletionTime], [b].[DepartmentId], [b].[IsDeleted], [b].[LastModificationTime], [b].[LastModifierUserId], [b].[Name], [t].[Id], [t].[CreationTime], [t].[CreatorUserId], [t].[DeleterUserId], [t].[DeletionTime], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[LastModificationTime], [t].[LastModifierUserId], [t].[Name]
